div.div:
- New state will calculate Ride price and will put that amount on hold
- There are two types of cancelations:
No charge/refund:
* When the driver has not been confirmed after 2 minutes and the passenger doesn't want to wait longer
* When there are no drivers available and no one confirms after 3 minutes
* When the driver has confirmed but will take longer to get to the passenger's location than expected
Ride will be charged:
* When the driver arrives to the passenger's location but passenger doesn't get into the car in a 5 minutes period
* When the passenger cancels the ride and the driver is on their way and will arrive to the passenger's location under 3 minutes
* When the passenger is not giving the correct one time token when getting into the car to the driver (means the driver never picked up the correct passenger)
